item.title: Help plese..about my rs 508 hd fullsreen server..? jdk help?
item.dc:creator: @unknown0154 unknown0154
item.description:
@unknown0154 wrote:

To set your variables do it like this first open up my computer->View system information->Advanced->Environmental Variables. Now you will have a screen on the bottom there is a button called New, Click it
For the name type CLASSPATH and the Variable value like this C:\Program Files\Java\jdkx.x.x_xx\bin
Now click path which is ALREADY on the list rename it to : PATH and type in the same thing as the CLASSPATH. If this doesn’t work for you go to search on the forums and type in Environmental Values Because there is many ways to do this.
